properties.Name: Stasiun Kereta Api
properties.Description: Jl. Mastrip, Blitar, Jawa Timur 66117 Train transit here : Penataran Dhoho, Matarmaja, Majapahit, Gajayana, Malabar, and Malioboro Express. Find the schedule on the web.

properties.Name: Bus Terminal Patria
properties.Description: You can find bus that go to Malang, Kepanjen, Talun, Kediri, Surabaya, Pare, Denpasar, and Jakarta.

properties.Name: Candi Penataran
properties.Description: Hinduism Temple that was build on Kediri kingdom era is the biggest temple in East java.

properties.Name: Makam Bung Karno
properties.Description: Jl. Ir. Soekarno, Blitar, Jawa Timur - 68113. In this place you can find the grave of The First President of Indonesia (Sang Proklamator), Ir. Soekarno. Also his mother, Ida Ayu Nyoman Rai, and his father, Raden Soekemi Sosrodiharjo.

properties.Name: Istana Gebang
properties.Description: House of First President of Indonesia, Soekarno. Jl. Sultan Agung No 69, Sanan Wetan Blitar.

properties.Name: Pesanggrahan Djojodigdan
properties.Description: House of Patih Djojodigdo (read: joyodigdo), one of local patriot and a loyal follower of Pangeran Diponegoro. He is parent in law of R.A Kartini.

properties.Name: Monumen PETA
properties.Description: Jln. Sudanco Supriyadi, Blitar. This monument was build in front of PETA army post. PETA i(Pembela Tanah Air)  was an Indonesian volunteer army established on1943 by the occupying Japanese. The Japanese intended PETA to assist their forces oppose a possible invasion by the Allies.

properties.Name: UPT Perpustakaan Proklamator Bung Karno
properties.Description: Jl. Ir. Soekarno, Blitar. This library has many collection of books especially related to Soekarno literature.

properties.Name: Masjid Agung
properties.Description: Jl. Masjid No 13, Blitar. A mosque that build on 1820, the witness of the historical development of islam in Blitar.

properties.Name: Warung Mbok Bari 6
properties.Description: Nasi Pecel Khas Blitar. Jl. Ir Soekarno No 93, Blitar. Pecel is one of the legendary culinary from this town. You must try it!

properties.Name: Es Mini 2
properties.Description: One of best cafe for your culinary trip. Offering dessert which call es mini, using many fruits as the ingredient. So fresh!

properties.Name: Taman Kota Kebon Rojo
properties.Description: A small recration park, free for visitors. In this park, there is  a few of animals such as merak bird, deer, monkey.

properties.Name: Alun Alun Blitar
properties.Description: Activity center of the town, every event will be held in here. People always visit here for short vacation, exercising or just hang out with family and friend.
